I would happily take the original rework plank back. 

Get rid of true damage, give us back melee kiting. Make raise morale castable while moving. 

Managing grog stacks and kiting to engineer winning trades in lane was far more enjoyable and engaging then barrel chains ever were. And instead of being pirate nasus, where I ignore teamfighting until I have my required minutes of farming, I actually had some team utility. {{sticker:zombie-brand-clap}} {{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
